ze: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.可更换后台模板，提供对应的后台模板（bootstrap），可让酱油君为您更换。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.对于找工作的童鞋，本站愿意提供服务器与域名，将您的后台管理系统项目解析到网上，让你在找工作期间能随时展示您的项目。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">安装与使用</span></strong></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px;\">[文档]<a href=\"http://www.yii-china.com/doc/hyii2.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"hyii2后台管理系统-文档\" textvalue=\"hyii2后台管理系统文档\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">hyii2后台管理系统文档</a></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px;\">[视频]</span><a href=\"http://www.yii-china.com/video/list/3.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"hyii2后台管理系统-视频\" textvalue=\"hyii2后台管理系统视频\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); outline: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">hyii2后台管理系统视频</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">功能简介</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">基础功能：</strong>登录，登出，密码修改等常见的功能</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">菜单配置：</strong>可视化配置菜单，可以根据配置用户的权限显示隐藏菜单（<a href=\"http://www.yii-china.com/video/list/3.html\" target=\"_self\" title=\"hyii2视频演示\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">观看视频</a>）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">权限机制：</strong>角色、权限增删改查，以及给用户赋予角色权限</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">规则机制：</strong>除了权限角色之外有规则机制，即可以给对应的权限配置规则</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">扩展组件：</strong>内置yii2各类扩展组件以及相应的效果演示（定时更新）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">6.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">二次开发：</strong>还在自己写权限？快使用hyii2做二次开发，只需写业务代码就能快速开发一套适合自己的后台管理系统</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">7.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内容管理：</strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">新增内容管理模块，分类管理，文章管理（已去除）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">8.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">模态编辑：</strong>模态框形式的创建与编辑（已去除）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">9.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">三级菜单：</strong>添加顶部菜单（hyii2模板）方便菜单根据业务进行分类</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">10.<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">模板切换：</strong>一键切换模板功能（hyii2模板与ace模板)</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px;\">效果图：</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160505/1462418661105485.png\" title=\"1462418661105485.png\" alt=\"NS9_E4IO5XJ_96US)95)MOT.png\" width=\"831\" height=\"527\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 831px; height: 527px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">登录页</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160507/1462560466733114.jpg\" title=\"1462560466733114.jpg\" alt=\"M_A8EYXVCWHZB2Q3I`Z}IEV.jpg\" width=\"830\" height=\"598\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 830px; height: 598px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">模态框形式编辑</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160613/1465809486477961.png\" title=\"1465809486477961.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" width=\"829\" height=\"534\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 829px; height: 534px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20161128/1480326606921257.png\" title=\"1480326606921257.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" width=\"829\" height=\"634\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 829px; height: 634px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20161128/1480326672591264.png\" title=\"1480326672591264.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" width=\"827\" height=\"592\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 827px; height: 592px;\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '/image/20180123/1516679153338315.png', '1', '561', 'test', '1', '1516679159', '1516679159');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES ('24', '基于Yii2的商城系统 - Yeshop [基础教程]', '简介Yeshop系统是在Yincart2 Galaxy基础上基于Yii2.0开发的“在线商城系统”，适合作为商城二次开发的基础系统，该系统包括前台、后台两套子系统。各个功能实现模块', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体;\">简介</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-indent: 28px;\">Yeshop系统是</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-indent: 28px;\">在Yincart2 Galaxy基础上基于Yii2.0开发的“在线商城系统”，适合作为商城二次开发的基础系统，该系统包括前台、后台两套子系统。各个功能实现模块化，模块间耦合度低，便于用户快速开发出符合自己需求的商城。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-indent: 28px;\">### 公共模块</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-indent: 28px;\">star-modules</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">acount&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 帐号管理模块（未使用）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">aftersales&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 售后模块，支持简单售后&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">refund&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ///售后模块，未完成(退换货)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">auth&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&