idth: 1075px; height: 750px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PS: 就像文章开篇说的，该商城系统是在yincart2的基础上修改的，因为galaxy是免费版，所以功能不完整且有很多潜在bug和待优化的地方，但本系统已经做进一步完善和功能扩展，大家可以放心使用，使用中遇到任何问题都可以联系我们。有兴趣的朋友也可以去百度上搜索yincart2下载源码自行学习。</p><p><br/></p>', '/image/20180123/1516679263711745.jpg', '2', '561', 'test', '1', '1516679291', '1516679291');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES ('25', 'YII2.0框架， 多图片上传功能 [基础教程]', '此小部件实现了文章或项目添加的时候，可以传多张图片，也以对上传成功的图片进行删除（如果配置项 trueDelete 为真， 则服务器上的真实图片也会删除）此小部件不能在上传图片的时', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">此小部件实现了文章或项目添加的时候，可以传多张图片，也以对上传成功的图片进行删除（如果配置项 trueDelete 为真， 则服务器上的真实图片也会删除）</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">此小部件不能在上传图片的时候， 选N张图片，只能一张一张的选择进行上传</p><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 24px 0px 16px; font-size: 36px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(234, 236, 239);\">安装说明</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">将下载的文件夹放入公共目录，本实例路径为（/common/widgets/），请根据项目实例自行安排， UploadAction.php文件内有使用说明，请进行参考。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">config:</span></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">use&nbsp;yii\\helpers\\Url;\r\n\r\nreturn&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/*&nbsp;上传图片配置项&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;fieldName&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&quot;fileData&quot;,&nbsp;/*&nbsp;提交的图片表单名称&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;maxSize&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;2097152,&nbsp;/*&nbsp;上传大小限制，单位B&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;allowFiles&#39;=&gt;&nbsp;[&quot;.png&quot;,&nbsp;&quot;.jpg&quot;,&nbsp;&quot;.jpeg&quot;,&nbsp;&quot;.gif&quot;,&nbsp;&quot;.bmp&quot;],&nbsp;/*&nbsp;上传图片格式显示&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;pathFormat&#39;=&gt;&nbsp;&quot;/uploads/{yyyy}/{mm}/{dd}/{date}{rand:6}&quot;,&nbsp;/*&nbsp;上传保存路径,可以自定义保存路径和文件名格式&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;uploadFilePath&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;str_replace(&#39;backend&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;frontend&#39;,&nbsp;$_SERVER[&#39;DOCUMENT_ROOT&#39;]),&nbsp;/*&nbsp;文件保存绝对路径&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;uploadType&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;upload&#39;,&nbsp;//remote远程图片&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;base64&nbsp;base64编码&nbsp;upload&nbsp;正常的上传方法,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;serverUrl&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;Url::to(&#39;/admin/upload/upload_more&#39;),\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;trueDelete&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;true&#39;&nbsp;//为TRUE是，点确定后，&nbsp;将会把真实图片删除，为false时，&nbsp;只会把父元素移除，&nbsp;不会删除真实图片\r\n];</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">controller:</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span><br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">public&nbsp;function&nbsp;actions()&nbsp;{\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;upload_more&#39;=&gt;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;common\\widgets\\batch_upload\\UploadAction&#39;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><span data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span><br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">view:</p><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Menlo, Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 3px;\">&lt;?=$form-&gt;field($model,&nbsp;&#39;pics&#39;)-&gt;widget(&#39;common\\widgets\\batch_upload\\FileUpload&#39;)?&gt;</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">上传图片插件为AjaxUpload3.9，无刷新上传图片，使用前， 请查看config.php进行配置，默认【图片表单名称】为fileData</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">#实现预览</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">功能实现</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zl0314/Yii2-batch-upload/blob/master/screenshot/pic1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/zl0314/Yii2-batch-upload/raw/master/screenshot/pic1.jpg\" alt=\"image\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">小部件存放目录</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; margin-bottom: 0px !important;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zl0314/Yii2-batch-upload/blob/master/screenshot/pic2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(3, 102, 214); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/zl0314/Yii2-batch-upload/raw/master/screenshot/pic2.jpg\" alt=\"image\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p><br/></p>', '/image/20180123/1516679354107407.jpg', '2', '561', 'test', '1', '1516679390', '1516679390');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES ('26', 'YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统 [基础教程]', 'YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统：git地址：https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git只有backend(后台)安装', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">YiiCMS 一个基于yii2写的后台基础内容管理系统：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">git地址：<a href=\"https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git\" _src=\"https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">https://coding.net/u/GitRong/p/YiiCMS/git</a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">只有backend(后台)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">安装：</p><ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">首先下载下来或者用git克隆下来.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">安装composer,并确保全局安装了&#39;composer-asset-plugin&#39;.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p></li><li><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">cd&nbsp;YiiCMS/</pre></li><li><pre style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">composer&nbsp;install</pre></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">在common/config/main-local下配置数据库信息.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">新建数据库并导入data/yiidemoad.sql的表结构以及数据.</p></li><li><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">配置虚拟主机指向backend/web目录并配置好hosts文件域名解析</p></li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">OK！安装完毕。打开虚拟域名即可访问.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20161010/1476079882371405.png\" title=\"1476079882371405.png\" alt=\"QQ截图20161010140223.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '/image/20180123/1516679431348729.jpg', '2', '561', 'test', '1', '1516679470', '1516679470');
INSERT INTO `posts` VALUES ('27', 'yii2 右键菜单扩展 yii2-contextmenu [扩展组件]', '&nbsp; &nbsp; 向大家推荐一个扩展：yii2-contextmenu， 该扩展为Gird行右击菜单，可以省去操作列。 扩展安装还是比较简单的，英文好的的朋友可以直接去h', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 向大家推荐一个扩展：yii2-contextmenu， 该扩展为Gird行右击菜单，可以<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">省去操作列</strong>。 扩展安装还是比较简单的，英文好的的朋友可以直接去<a href=\"https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu\" target=\"_blank\" textvalue=\"https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu</a>上查看，然后按着它操作就好了。懒得去看英文的同学，那就看我吧：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 相信大家都知道用composer安装方便，差不多一键搞定。不过国内composer访问实在慢的蛋疼，所以我建议大家直接在上面的链接里下载zip文件手动加载扩展，手动也快的。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1、下载zip:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu/archive/master.zip\" target=\"_blank\" textvalue=\"https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu/archive/master.zip\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; outline: none; cursor: pointer;\">https://github.com/phpyii/yii2-contextmenu/archive/master.zip</a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2、解压后重名名为yii2-contextmenu</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、在vendor下新建文件夹liyunfang，把yii2-contextmenu丢进去。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4、修改vendor/yiisoft/extensions.php，在最数组最后面追加一项：&nbsp;</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;liyunfang/yii2-contextmenu&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;array&nbsp;(\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;name&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;liyunfang/yii2-contextmenu&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;version&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;9999999-dev&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;alias&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;array&nbsp;(\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;@liyunfang/contextmenu&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$vendorDir&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;/liyunfang/yii2-contextmenu&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;),</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; OK了， 扩展加载完毕，接下来就是如果使用扩展了。</p><pre class=\"brush:php;toolbar:false\" deep=\"5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.42857; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;?=&nbsp;GridView::widget([\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;dataProvider&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$dataProvider,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;filterModel&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$searchModel,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;columns&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;\\kartik\\grid\\CheckboxColumn&#39;],&nbsp;&nbsp;//第0列\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//第1列\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;class&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;\\liyunfang\\contextmenu\\SerialColumn::className(),\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;contextMenu&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;true,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&#39;contextMenuAttribute&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;id&#39;,\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;buttons&#39;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;view&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;function&nbsp;($url,&nbsp;$model){\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$title&nbsp;=&nbsp;Yii::t(&#39;kvgrid&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;View&#39;);\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$label&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;&lt;span&nbsp;class=&quot;glyphicon&nbsp;glyphicon-eye-open&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&#39;&nbsp;.&nbsp;$title;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$options&nbsp;=&nbsp;[&#39;tabindex&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;-1&#39;,&nbsp;&#39;title&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;$title,&nbsp;&#39;data&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;[&#39;pjax&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;0&#39;&nbsp;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;toggle&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;tooltip&#39;],&nbsp;&#39;target&#39;=&gt;&#39;_blank&#39;];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;&#39;&lt;li&gt;&#39;&nbsp;.&nbsp;Html::a($label,&nbsp;$url,&nbsp;$options)&nbsp;.&nbsp;&#39;&lt;/li&gt;&#39;&nbsp;.&nbsp;PHP_EOL;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;......&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//第n列&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;、、\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;......\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;],\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;rowOptions这里也要设置\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;rowOptions&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;function($model,&nbsp;$key,&nbsp;$index,&nbsp;$gird){\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$contextMenuId&nbsp;=&nbsp;$gird-&gt;columns[1]-&gt;contextMenuId;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;[&#39;data&#39;=&gt;[&nbsp;&#39;toggle&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;&#39;context&#39;,&#39;target&#39;=&gt;&nbsp;&quot;#&quot;.$contextMenuId&nbsp;]];\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;},\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;......\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;......</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;PS:&nbsp; rowOptions 对应的闭包函数中， $gird-&gt;columns[1]-&gt;contextMenuId;&nbsp; columns的下标值指的是<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">列号</strong>。第0列是&nbsp;[&#39;class&#39; =&gt; &#39;\\kartik\\grid\\CheckboxColumn&#39;],&nbsp; 第1列才是正确的值，这个大家在用的时候注意下。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;结束，扩展安装和扩展使用介绍完毕。最后我想说个题外话，这个扩展应该是一个叫liyunfang的哥们写的，刚开始看到这个namespace liyunfang\\contextmenu; 就有种抵触情绪，怕国产扩展不好，所以去看了下源码， 看完后决定用它了， 觉得写的还不错，赞！支持国产插件。我媚外了</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最后贴一张效果图：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://up.yii-china.com/image/20160927/1474961848455535.png\" title=\"1474961848455535.png\" alt=\"QQ图片20160927153829.png\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p><br/></p>', '/image/20180123/1516679729636440.png', '1', '561', 'test', '1', '1516679755', '1516679755');

